{"tid":37063,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[索尼罪大滔天] 強烈建議巴打們唔好買Sony機","createTime":"2016-12-13T06:10:59.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-13T06:15:21.000Z","uid":42469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"11c2e112b30c0ab228b3b62f3f5e099e6fce2546","tid":37063,"uid":42469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T06:10:59.000Z","msg":"原來Sony mobile係無香港分部<br />\nSony HK就係TSO，咁TSO既服務有幾差我都唔洗多講<br />\n我部機保養期內已經整左八次，最後一次比佢地整穿埋防水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n八次搭車排隊夾埋浪費左我超過30個鐘<br />\n最後一次TSO counter叫佢換機馬上黑臉淨係講無咁既服務<br />\n叫佢搵大佬跟就話自己就係大佬<br />\n<br />\n屌佢一send信上Sony Global就換得機，個TSO真係on撚鳩無柒用<br />\n點知原來Sony Global只係redirect我封信去TSO投訴部<br />\n問佢點解啲員工完全唔肯幫我，佢就話會跟進改善，有問題可以打黎<br />\n屌你老母我睇勻成間TSO我都見唔到有投訴部電話<br />\n<br />\n同佢講我要延長埋保養就reject我，淨係肯換機<br />\n機我就會照換，訴我會繼續投<br />\n已經決定send上去Sony CEO個email到<br />\nKazuo.Hirai@jp.sony.com<br />\nSony機好唔好講唔出，但Sony係香港既售後我敢講就屎都不如<br />\n<br />\n講咁多都係想勸各位巴打<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">咪撚買Sony啊!</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c20f8e805af5b80768b2fcec43aeed61033aedbf","tid":37063,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-13T06:11:33.000Z","msg":"啱"},{"pid":"bdb9b0880ac2270078e1e94b6378b472b677545a","tid":37063,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTi